                     <interp inst="t18310407-99-off551" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310407-99-cd552" type="crimeDate">19th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310407-99-off551 t18310407-99-cd552"></join>, 1 butter-boat, value 3l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18310407-99-victim887" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Grainger
                  <interp inst="t18310407-99-victim887" type="surname" value="Grainger"></interp>
